1 plan upon the expiration or termination of the vesting rights period provided
2 for in this section.
3 (3) Notwithstanding any provision of this section, the establishment of a vested
4 right does not preclude, change, or impair the authority of a local government
5 to adopt and enforce development regulations governing nonconforming
6 situations or uses.
